description:
Verify the existing Python toolchain mapping in mappings.nix works correctly.

Current mapping:
```nix
python = {
  skip = false;
  targets = [{
    name = "python_bootstrap";
    rule = "system_python_bootstrap_toolchain";
    load = "@prelude//toolchains:python.bzl";
    visibility = [ "PUBLIC" ];
  }];
  implicitDependencies = [ ];
};
```

Verify:
1. Adding `python = {}` to toolchain.toml adds python to toolchains cell
2. The generated BUCK file has correct python toolchain target
3. `buck2 build` can use the python toolchain for python targets
